## Type hints

- use `from __future__ import annotations`, it cleans up and future proofs the code
- convert generic dict[str, Any] types into more specific dataclasses
- get rid of Any types whenever possible
- restructure mission setup to avoid needing `assert Foo is not None` constructs
- make sure that typing.cast instances are guaranteed to return the correct type
- implement 'evaluate_model' for hawk.scout.trainer.{fsl,yolo}.model:Model

